<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202964>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Hyalella carsone sp. nov., municipality of Bocaina do Sul, state of Santa Catarina (27°44′4.4″S 49°59′1.0″W). Paratype male, 6.75 mm, CCUFLA 449. (A) Pleopod. (B) Uropod 1. (C) Uropod 2. (D) Uropod 3. (E) and (F) Telson. Scale bars: A and B—0.4 mm; C to F—0.2 mm." ;
