    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Schematic plate. (A) Aesthetascs present on antenna 1 of Hyalella carsone sp. nov. (B) Aesthetascs present on antenna 1 of Hyalella wangarie sp. nov. (C) Schematic serrate seta subtype F3 based on Zimmer et al. (2009). (D) The new type of seta serrate with accessory seta." ;
